response.original_title: Chikara Man Makes Plans, And God Laughs
response.overview: September 12th, 2009  Claudio Castagnoli and Hallowicked put on a technical wrestling clinic! The seemingly familiar duo of The Badd Boyz arrive and make their presence felt. Tim Donst dominates his former tag team partner, Hydra! Ophidian returns from injury as the The Osirian Portal takes on F.I.S.T. in tag team action. Matches featured:  1. Brendan Michael Thomas vs Frightmare  2. The Badd Boys vs The Colony  3. Grizzly Redwood vs Steve "The Turtle" Weiner  4. Colin Delaney vs Dasher Hatfield  5. The Order Of The Neo Solar Temple vs Super Smash Brothers  6. Tim Donst vs Hydra  7. The UnStable & Daizee Haze vs Mike Quackenbush, Lince Dorado & Equinox  8. The Osirian Portal vs F.I.S.T.  9. Hallowicked vs Claudio Castagnoli
response.title: Chikara Man Makes Plans, And God Laughs
